00:00:25.439 --> 00:00:29.339
and I realized that we actually have a very
fundamentally shared value, or fundamentally

00:00:29.339 --> 00:00:34.970
shared important value which is the idea of
creating opportunities for everybody and making

00:00:34.970 --> 00:00:39.450
the world more flat and creating opportunities
for people who maybe used to be disenfranchised.

00:00:39.450 --> 00:00:43.960
