really grasp the meaning of at the time and

00:08:18.449 --> 00:08:22.340
now I know that they've made all the difference
in the world because when you have parents

00:08:22.340 --> 00:08:26.479
that care, you have a foundation set for you.

00:08:26.479 --> 00:08:31.610
And that is something that I was very lucky
to have that a lot of my friends in the community

00:08:31.610 --> 00:08:34.159
